Super Smooth Treatments











Hair Smoothing Keratin Treatments
Keratin Complex’s signature hair smoothing treatments offer a keratin treatment smoothing solution for every hair type, lifestyle and budget. Our keratin treatments also vary with regard to time in the salon, longevity of results, and the waiting period to shampoo or style post-treatment.
Remember:
A consultation with your stylist will help to determine which Keratin Complex smoothing service is best for you.
Find a Salon








Service Key:    Treatment Cost    Time Spent in Salon    Waiting Period Time    Longevity of Results 






						Natural Keratin Smoothing Treatment™




The Signature
Smoothing Solution
					
Featuring Natural Keratin Smoothing Treatment™
Best For:
Any hair type with frizz and/or curl seeking the longest-lasting smoothness, manageability and protection against humidity.



Higher cost



More time spent in salon



72-hour waiting period



Results last up to 5 months








						Natural Keratin Smoothing Treatment
						for Blonde Hair
					



The Signature Smoothing
					Solution For Fragile Hair
Featuring Natural Keratin Smoothing Treatment for Blonde Hair
Best For:
Any hair type with frizz and/or curl that needs extra care and conditioning—such as fragile or overprocessed hair—and still wants the longest-lasting results.



Higher cost



More time spent in salon



72-hour waiting period



Results last up to 5 months








						Express Blow Out™




The Speedy
Smoothing Solution
					
Featuring Express Blow Out™
Best For:
Any hair type with frizz and/or curl looking for a quick smoothing solution.



Low cost



Less time spent in salon



8-hour waiting period



Results last up to 1.5 months








						Personalized Blow Out™
					


Personalized Blow Out™
Your Hair. Your Way.
						Go straight or stay curly (and everything in between)
Styled Finishes
						Best For:
Any hair type looking to smooth or straighten the hair and increase manageability with zero downtime.
Natural Curl Finish
						Best For:
Any client with natural texture that is looking to define curl, increase manageability and reduce frizz.


Medium cost



Medium time spent in salon



No waiting period



Results last up to 3 months





Contact your stylist to help determine which Keratin Complex smoothing service is best for you!
Find a Salon
Disclaimer: All information herein is based on current scientific research and is subject to change based on new findings.














