			Money Back refund request must be postmarked a minimum of 120 days after sales receipt purchase date. Submissions postmarked before 120 days from sales receipt purchase date will not be honored. 
3. The original ROGAINE® product UPC (s) from the package(s).
Receive:
A refund for the purchase price of your Men's ROGAINE® product(s) or Women's ROGAINE® product(s) up to $94.00 (including tax)
Mail To:
ROGAINE® Brand Money Back Guarantee, Johnson & Johnson Consumer Care Center - 5th floor, 120 N Commercial St, Neenah, WI 54956
Offer Terms valid for U.S. residents only. Purchase must be made 1/16/17 through 12/31/17 and reimbursement claim received at the mailing address on or before 7/31/18. Offer is limited to one (1) reimbursement claim per household or street address for the purchase of any of the following combinations:


